title.narrative: Plan and implement a comprehensive programme to prevent re-establishment of malaria in the Democratic Republic of Timor-Leste

description.narrative: Timor-Leste - Malaria - Ministry of Health of the Democratic Republic of Timor-Leste - MOH. This program has the following goals: To remain free of indigenous malaria. The objectives of this program are: To prevent re-establishment of malaria transmission in Timor-Leste. To maintain zero mortality due to locally acquired malaria. To achieve WHO malaria free certification
